        "timestamp": 1751225423
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>For this particular case you can also use <code>contradiction</code> and it will find the <code>False.elim</code> in your tactic state and extract the proof of <code>False</code>.</p>",
        "id": 526289971,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1751225603
    },
    {
